n (獲益) and loss (損失) are to be construed as extending not only to gain or loss in money or other property, but as extending to any such gain or loss whether temporary or permanent; and&mdash;<br />\n(a)gain (獲益) includes a gain by keeping what one has, as well as a gain by getting what one has not; and<br />\n(b)loss (損失) includes a loss by not getting what one might get, as well as a loss by parting with what one has."},{"pid":"0319f1c19816126542df3f85d98cb0e05f62b826","tid":774752,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e65109ba0853525fb43cec11ab3281fd2127448","tid":774752,"uid":76471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57cedcf1c46b9888425d9ba7b2be028ceeb93a03","tid":774752,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecb4df5e35eb58404c583f9c9eb1e940a2391498","tid":774752,"uid":76471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T18:12:57.000Z","msg":"調返轉，邊章邊節講正常角度，距離，明影會犯法？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T18:16:05.000Z","msg":"我就係唔識，想學嘢<br />\n問個警察佢話係新聞自由"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T18:27:38.000Z","msg":"唔關新聞自由事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係偷拍裙底相同走光相分別，你會唔會見狗仔隊擺部相機係裙底影相"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T00:29:14.000Z","msg":"狗仔隊咪就係擺部相機對住裙底影相囉<br />\n<br />\n唔係邊有麥明詩裙底相?<br />\n<br />\n你條柒頭一味係度鳩 UP,  按你自己既想像去發明法律<br />\n仲要係度持續地柒"},{"pid":"c745dedec8bce555b51749fb5604fadb19ac3786","tid":774752,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T00:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}